     & 4*4.0,                  10.0,  3.0,
     & 5.0, 8.0, 4*6.0  /

C  ( Ortho-phosphate (µgP/l)        NOT USED):
C   means:
C      DATA PO4NM /
C     & 20.0, 21.0, 16.0, 12.0,  5.0,  5.0,
